#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The background graphics <quote>starfield</quote> was taken from the <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.gimp.org/\">Gimp</ulink>. All other graphics were created "
"by &Anders.Widell; &Anders.Widell.mail; using the <ulink url=\"https://www."
"povray.org/\">Povray</ulink> ray tracer."
msgstr ""
"De achtergrond <quote>starfield</quote> is afkomstig uit <ulink url="
"\"https://www.gimp.org/\">Gimp</ulink>. Alle andere afbeeldingen zijn "
"gemaakt door &Anders.Widell; &Anders.Widell.mail; met behulp van de <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.povray.org/\">Povray</ulink> ray tracer."

